Dear Colleague:
<p><%= @sender.person_forename%> <%= @sender.person_surname%>, <%= @sender.person_role%> with <%= @appname%> has requested we send you a message on the following subject: <%= @message.subject %>.</p>
<p>The message content is provided at the bottom of this email.<p>
<p>Please DO NOT REPLY to this email.</p>
<p>You are requested to log into the Members website <a href="https://<%=@host%>"> <%= @host%> </a>
(if not already logged in) to review the message there. </p>
<p>On the initial landing page after the log in; select the "Messages" button and on the list of messages select the "Show" for specific message identification <%=@message.identifier%>.</p>
<p>In many cases you will be able reply to the originator of the message by selecting the "Reply" button at the top of the message being displayed.</p>
<p>The following is the message content:</p>
<p>  <%= @message.body %></p>
<p><%= @signature[:u_name] %></p>
<p><%= @signature[:u_role]%></p>
<p>The <%= @appname %> Team.</p>
<p>Free UK Genealogy</p>